Petugas medis!

329
00:35:51,189 --> 00:35:56,319
Semuanya akan baik saja. Bill.
Ini bukan apa-apa. Semua akan beres.

330
00:35:59,155 --> 00:36:00,114
Ini bukan apa-apa.

331
00:36:03,910 --> 00:36:06,371
Berengsek. Petugas medis!

332
00:36:08,122 --> 00:36:10,124
Rupanya kau di situ.

333
00:36:10,833 --> 00:36:12,377
Tekan.

334
00:36:14,921 --> 00:36:16,339
- Maaf.
- Apa?

335
00:36:22,303 --> 00:36:23,888
- Bill.
- Bantu aku membawanya.

336
00:36:25,056 --> 00:36:25,973
Bill.

337
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,103
Bill.

338
00:36:55,211 --> 00:36:57,171
Berengsek, itu tank Jepang.

339
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:02,760
Tentara, tembakkan beberapa HE
pada para berengsek itu.

340
00:37:05,263 --> 00:37:08,516
- Sekarang. Ayo cepat.
- Kalian dengar kata Letnan. Ayo.

341
00:37:08,599 --> 00:37:09,851
Cepat.

342
00:37:15,857 --> 00:37:18,151
Tunggu di sini.

343
00:37:20,069 --> 00:37:23,906
- Ini 76 meter.
- Tiga mortir HE.

344
00:37:32,039 --> 00:37:33,583
Amunisi.

345
00:37:35,001 --> 00:37:36,252
- Siap!
- Tembak!

346
